tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE transactions (
  transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  transaction_date DATE,
  sender_address VARCHAR(255),
  receiver_address VARCHAR(255),
  amount DECIMAL(10, 2)
)

CREATE TABLE regulatory_audit (
    audit_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    transaction_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    reason TEXT,
    auditor TEXT,
    audit_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE transactions ( 
    transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    transaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP, 
    sender_address VARCHAR(255), 
    receiver_address VARCHAR(255), 
    amount DECIMAL(18, 2) 
);
CREATE TABLE transactions ( transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY, transaction_date TIMESTAMP, transaction_amount DECIMAL(10, 2), sender_wallet_address TEXT, receiver_wallet_address TEXT );
CREATE TABLE wallets ( wallet_address TEXT PRIMARY KEY, wallet_balance DECIMAL(15, 2) );
CREATE TABLE users ( user_id INT PRIMARY KEY, username TEXT, email TEXT, phone_number TEXT );
CREATE TABLE blocks ( block_id INT PRIMARY KEY, block_hash TEXT, block_date TIMESTAMP );
CREATE TABLE regulations ( regulation_id INT PRIMARY KEY, regulation_name TEXT, regulation_description TEXT );
